@ajdapretnar That's probably my fault; I may have suggested that you no longer need a delegate when you removed the lines between documents.

You probably need

```
class HorizontalGridDelegate(QStyledItemDelegate):
    """Class for drawing horizontal line between documents."""
    def paint(self, painter, option, index):
        if index.column() == 0:
            option.textElideMode = Qt.ElideLeft
        elif index.column() == 2:
            option.textElideMode = Qt.ElideRight
        QStyledItemDelegate.paint(self, painter, option, index)
```

And then `self.conc_view.setItemDelegate(HorizontalGridDelegate())` when you set up the view.

